  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag

    public class ThymeleafTag
extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport

    Simple tag that allows rendering a Thymeleaf template from a JSP. Requires Thymeleaf support to be enabled and servlet-api to be present.

    Based on source code from org.thymeleaf.spring4.view.ThymeleafView

    .
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    org.thymeleaf.spring4.view.ThymeleafView, Serialized Form
